shown their victims any mercy...

207
00:20:05,145 --> 00:20:07,579
...but society has its judges.

208
00:20:07,748 --> 00:20:09,841
And I wasn't one of them.

209
00:20:10,217 --> 00:20:13,414
At the same time,
what did I have to do with all that?

210
00:20:13,587 --> 00:20:15,555
I had two choices;

211
00:20:15,722 --> 00:20:18,350
Forget or go back.

212
00:20:20,660 --> 00:20:22,287
Take a deep breath.

213
00:20:25,365 --> 00:20:26,491
Smoker?

214
00:20:26,666 --> 00:20:27,894
Just cigarettes.

215
00:20:28,702 --> 00:20:30,761
- No crack?
- Never.

216
00:20:31,505 --> 00:20:32,995
