Undress, everything!

1259
02:14:23,860 --> 02:14:26,124
- Undress!
- Heads down!

1260
02:17:16,700 --> 02:17:18,793
"Davilson, dearest son...

1261
02:17:20,103 --> 02:17:24,039
...your mother weeps when she thinks
of you when you were little...

1262
02:17:25,142 --> 02:17:27,770
...laughing deep into my eyes.

1263
02:17:29,312 --> 02:17:32,179
I know you never
believed in my God...

1264
02:17:32,682 --> 02:17:35,549
...but today, as I read the Bible...

1265
02:17:35,719 --> 02:17:39,052
...it was as if you were here
in my lap again.

1266
02:17:39,956 --> 02:17:44,325
My heart trembled as
I read Psalm 91.

1267
02:17:45,562 --> 02:17:48,053
What beautiful words.

1268
02:17:50,567 --> 02:17:55,266
A thousand may fall
at your right hand...

1269
02:17:56,206 --> 02:17:58,800
...but no evil will come near you...

1270
02:18:00,210 --> 02:18:02,678
...no scourge come near your tent."

1271
02:18:48,325 --> 02:18:53,627
In the late '80s, AIDS
prevention work in jails...

1272
02:18:53,797 --> 02:18:57,699
...took me to the São Paulo
Detention Center. Carandiru.

1273
02:18:58,235 --> 02:19:02,001
There I heard stories, made
real friends, learned medicine...

1274
02:19:02,172 --> 02:19:06,802
...and penetrated a few
of the mysteries of life in jail...

1275
02:19:06,977 --> 02:19:10,936
...which would have remained
inaccessible were I not a doctor.

1276
02:19:22,025 --> 02:19:24,016
- Morning, doctor.
- Good morning.

1277
02:19:26,897 --> 02:19:30,264
Even today, whenever I hear
the iron gates close behind me...

1278
02:19:30,433 --> 02:19:34,767
...I feel that shudder,
just like all those matinees...

1279
02:19:34,938 --> 02:19:39,568
...where I'd sit glued to my chair as
I watched all those jail films in B&W.

1280
02:19:42,545 --> 02:19:47,005
On October 2, 1992, 111 men died
at the São Paulo Detention Center.

1281
02:19:47,183 --> 02:19:49,913
There were no police deaths.

1282
02:19:50,086 --> 02:19:54,022
The only ones who know what
really happened are God...

1283
02:19:54,190 --> 02:19:56,988
...the police and the inmates.
I only heard the latter.

1284
02:19:59,562 --> 02:20:03,760
On September 15, 2002,
the last inmates were transferred.

1285
02:20:03,934 --> 02:20:06,300
Once empty, Carandiru
closed its doors.

1286
02:20:27,857 --> 02:20:33,386
On December 9, Carandiru
was finally demolished.


